<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 비밀번호 찾기</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/library.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="sub-hedaer">
            <button type="button" class="btn-back">뒤로가기</button>
            <h1 class="page-title">비밀번호 찾기</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-search">검색</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn-cart">장바구니</button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <div class="loginWrap">
            <div class="tab-a">
                <ul>
                    <li class="on"><a href="MU12_M_0204.html">휴대폰 본인인증</a></li>
                    <li><a href="MU12_M_0205_1.html">이메일 인증</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-cont">
                <div class="on">
                    <h3 class="login-title">
                        정보를 입력해 주세요.
                    </h3>
                    <div class="login-subText">
                        아이디와 본인 명의의 휴대폰 번호 인증을 통해<br>비밀번호를 재설정하실 수 있습니다.
                    </div>
                    <ul class="form-input mt30">
                        <li class="form-flex">
                            <div class="form-flex-cell">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="아이디 입력(email , 휴대폰번호)" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-flex-btn">
                                <button class="btn-basicM">확인</button>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="form-flex">
                            <div class="form-flex-cell">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="이름 입력" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-flex-select">
                                <select>
                                    <option>내국인</option>
                                    <option>외국인</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="form-flex">
                            <div class="form-flex-cell">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="생년월일 입력 (8자리)" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-flex-select">
                                <select>
                                    <option>남자</option>
                                    <option>여자</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="form-flex">
                            <div class="form-flex-cell">
                                <input type="text" placeholder="휴대폰 번호 입력 ( ‘-’ 제외)" />
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-flex-select">
                                <select>
                                    <option>SKT</option>
                                    <option>KT</option>
                                    <option>LGT</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="form-flex">
                            <div class="form-flex-cell">
                                <div class="verify-num">
                                    <input type="text" placeholder="인증번호 입력">
                                    <span>02:00</span>
                                    <button type="button">인증번호 재요청</button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="verify-message">
                                    인증 시간이 경과했습니다. 인증번호 재전송을 통해 인증을 다시 진행해 주세요.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <!-- accordionBox -->
                    <div class="accordionBox mt20">
                        <div class="accordion-title type2">
                            <label>
                                <input type="checkbox" class="type2">
                                <span>본인 인증을 위한 약관 모두 동의</span>
                            </label>
                            <button>열림</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="accordion-panel">
                            <div>
                                <ul class="form-check mt10">
                                    <li>
                                        <label class="chk-agree">
                                            <input type="checkbox">
                                            <span>(필수) 개인정보 수집 및 이용 동의</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <button>보기</button>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <label class="chk-agree">
                                            <input type="checkbox">
                                            <span>(필수) 고유식별정보 처리 동의</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <button>보기</button>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <label class="chk-agree">
                                            <input type="checkbox">
                                            <span>(필수) 통신사 이용약관</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <button>보기</button>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <label class="chk-agree">
                                            <input type="checkbox">
                                            <span>(필수) 서비스 이용약관</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <button>보기</button>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- //accordionBox -->

                    <div class="btnWrap">
                        <button class="btn-basicM fill">인증번호 전송</button>
                    </div>
                    <!-- <div class="btnWrap">
                        <button class="btn-basicM fill">확인</button>
                    </div> -->
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>